Package jsonvalues.gen

Class JsTupleGen

java.lang.Object
jsonvalues.gen.JsTupleGen
All Implemented Interfaces:
fun.gen.Gen<JsArray>, Function<Random,Supplier<JsArray>>
public final class JsTupleGen extends Object implements fun.gen.Gen<JsArray>
Represents a tuple generator that is modeled with an array generator where each index has its own generator. Each generator of the tuple is created from a new seed that is calculated passing the original one to the split generator .
